## Introduction
The purpose of this document is to define the technical architecture for Allio v1, aligning with the mission of Forgotten Formula PMA to prioritize healing over profits and nature over synthetic. This document serves as a blueprint for developers and stakeholders to understand the system's design, its components, and how they interact to fulfill our mission.


## System Overview
Allio v1 is designed to be a robust, scalable system that integrates modern technology to facilitate a healing-focused environment. The system leverages AI capabilities to enhance human decision-making in healthcare, ensuring member privacy and fostering sovereignty within the PMA framework.


